0.4:

2010-04-30  David King  <davidk@openismus.com>

	Extensive modernisation

	* Makefile.am: Non-recursive build and drop libtool hackery.
	* configure.ac: Drop all deprecated macros, use modern equivalents.
	* autogen.sh: Simplify.

